title: Retro Rocket Watch Face
summary: This swell watch face has a retro style rocket orbiting around your watch!
description: This space watch face is inspired by Disney's Tomorrowland. It features a rocket ship orbiting around planets surrounded by stars that mark the hours.New color options available now! With traditional watch face or orbiting rocketship in place of the second hand.If you're having trouble getting your watch face onto your Android Wear device, follow these instructions: http://apps.shameronstudios.com/how-to-setup-an-android-wear-watch-face/
descriptionHTML:
This space watch face is inspired by Disney's Tomorrowland. It features a rocket ship orbiting around planets surrounded by stars that mark the hours.

New color options available now! With traditional watch face or orbiting rocketship in place of the second hand.

If you're having trouble getting your watch face onto your Android Wear device, follow these instructions: http://apps.shameronstudios.com/how-to-setup-an-android-wear-watch-face/
comments: The Unofficial Watch face of Tomorrow's One of this Disneyland Cast Members favorite watch faces. Please consider designing a face for Jungle Cruise, Trains, Main Street Vehicles, Disneyland's 60th anniversary, etc.

recentChanges: v1.4: Adds support for Android Wear 2.0
Adds automatic switching between light and dark mode at 6PM and 6AM. Now your watch can be in dark mode at night and light mode during the day automatically!
Also updated ambient mode to look better on OLED screens.
